This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard the personal information of users ("User," "you," or "your") of our mobile application ("App"). We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. By using our App, you consent to the practices described in this Privacy Policy.
1. Information We Collect
1.1. Personal Information:
We may collect personal information that you voluntarily provide to us when you use our App, such as your name, email address, and any other information you provide.
1.2. Non-Personal Information:
We may collect non-personal information about your device, including but not limited to the type of mobile device you use, your device's unique device identifier, the IP address of your device, your mobile operating system, and information about the way you use the App.
2. How We Use Your Information
2.1. We may use the personal information you provide to:
- Provide and improve our services
- Respond to your inquiries and fulfill your requests
- Personalize and improve your experience with the App
- Send you administrative information, updates, and promotional materials related to the App
- Analyze usage of the App and improve its functionality
2.2. We may use non-personal information for various purposes, including:
- Analyzing trends and usage of the App
- Improving the App and its features
- Enhancing user experience
- Aggregating and anonymizing data for statistical purposes
3. How We Disclose Your Information
3.1. We may disclose your personal information:
- To third-party service providers who assist us in providing and improving our services (e.g., hosting services, analytics providers)
- To comply with applicable laws, regulations, or legal processes
- To protect and defend our rights or property, including enforcing our policies and terms of use
3.2. We may disclose non-personal information to third parties for various purposes, including but not limited to analytics, research, and marketing.
4. Third-Party Services and Links
Our App may contain links to third-party websites, services, or advertisements that are not owned or controlled by us. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of such third-party services. We encourage you to review the privacy policies of those third parties before providing any personal information.
5. Data Security
We employ reasonable security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
6. Children's Privacy
Our App is not intended for use by individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If we become aware that we have collected personal information from a child without parental consent, we will take steps to remove the information and terminate the child's account.
7. Changes to this Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting the revised policy. By continuing to use the App, you agree to the updated Privacy Policy.
8. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our privacy practices, please contact us at
appexosolutions@gmail.com
.
By using our App, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy and agree to the collection, use, and disclosure of your personal information as described herein.